1. Add a normal user

  useradd -m galma
  passwd galma
  
2. Add user to sudoers group

  visudo
  ---> Look for "User privilege specification" and "root ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL" 
  ---> Add a similar line i.e. "galma ALL=(ALL) ALL"
  
3. Install KDE 

  pacman -S xorg plasma-meta plasma-wayland-session kde-applications-meta 
  
4. Enable Display Manager & NetworkManager

  systemctl enable sddm
  
